    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The college is very supportive in the extra curicular activities and sports",
          "name": "Lokeshwaran R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "environment is good and peaceful and silent .",
          "name": "Lokeshwaran R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placements are decent with more than 80% students who opted for placement get placed",
          "name": "Harshavardhan M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Decent Dress code been Implemented. The college had strict dress code, But Fairly it was exercised last year, Allowing T shirts and jeans with some restricted allowance",
          "name": "Harshavardhan M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching is Good in my college. Most of the professors have hands on exposure to every experimental methods based on their field of teaching",
          "name": "Harshavardhan M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "This college provides importance to the sports .",
          "name": "Srinivasan",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The facilities are so good and friendly just like our parents",
          "name": "Harshan A",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Books and journals have been ready available we can able to read any time",
          "name": "OM PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Superb faculty members they were teaching really well",
          "name": "OM PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus was very neat and cleaned structure in college",
          "name": "OM PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Long distance from the city . And traffic during travel",
          "name": "Reshmi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I really disappointed about the campus interview",
          "name": "Udaykumar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Food quality is bit compromised ,hostel students find it very difficult",
          "name": "Mythreye",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College is in the out skirts of the city amd hence it takes a long time to travel",
          "name": "Kiran muthuselvam",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lack of proper communication between staffs and management",
          "name": "Harshavardhan M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Staffs hesitate in providing lecture notes and ppts. They only provide the lecture notes at the neck of the moment Only for reference and will ask us to study from books (This will be primarily deployed from 2nd year)",
          "name": "Harshavardhan M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fetches a lot of money in the name of placement.",
          "name": "Srinivasan",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "When the hostellers need to go home the gatepass procedure is so bad and it's time consuming",
          "name": "Harshan A",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The main reason is the food provided in the college hostels",
          "name": "Harshan A",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sports development was very lease in case.",
          "name": "OM PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ]
    },
